title: Shirley Ceaser Gospel
description:
This is not an album. It's a mixture of some very old and a few hard to find Shirley Ceaser songs. I noticed that this site doesn't begin to enough gospel songs. so folks, Enjoy.

12 tracks.
Rejoice
Lift Him UP
God Specializes
Nicodemus
Armour Of God
He's Working it out
Peace In the Midst Of The storm
Strong Man
You Can Make It
Don't Drive Mama Away
He'll Do It Again
